{"tid":1913767,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本土研究社又爆料：竹篙灣及鯉魚門「隔離營」隨時變成有毒豆腐渣工程","createTime":"2020-03-07T05:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T05:31:59.000Z","uid":255105,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb0601224208069ef5b823bb32137f38bce0c0b","tid":1913767,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:11:07.000Z","msg":"【中資醫護設施工程播毒威水史】<br />\n<br />\n可能大家沒留意海外新聞，今次獲林鄭獎券基金直接批億元起竹篙灣及鯉魚門「隔離營」的中交建系國企 (包括中國港灣及中國建築)，其實近年不少醫護設施工程都「揚威海外」，例如近日就被澳洲政府發現中交建子公司John Holland於塔斯曼尼亞的新重建Royal Hobart Hospital醫院大樓鉛水超標，現時工程已無限期擱置，【註一】本地幾乎無任何消息及報導。<br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶，全中資擁有的John Holland，於2016年承建澳洲柏斯兒童醫院時同樣有鉛水超標。更嚴重是，還被澳洲工人揭發醫院內的隔熱板含一級致癌物料石棉 (想知石棉有幾恐怖可參考 : <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3ayLqYZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ayLqYZ&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnEigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=be7224be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3ayLqYZ</a> ) ，引起公眾恐慌，整間醫院立即被隔離【註二】。<br />\n<br />\n其後澳國透過資訊自由(FOI)追查原因，發現John Holland引入了中交建長期合作的供應商「中國遠大」的建材物料出事，其後中國遠大事後解釋它們也並不知情，是其他背後中國供應商的問題【註三】，播毒事件亦無從問責。<br />\n<br />\n記得2015年同期，中國建築都有在香港牽起了啟德鉛水風波，其後政府試圖幫手將問題歸咎一名水喉匠使用含鉛焊料【註四】，所以一切只是水喉匠的錯，不關中資及背後中資建材供應鏈的事。<br />\n<br />\nJohn Holland作為中國一帶一路併購外地工程公司「走出去」的重要佈署，很清楚的顯示出中資國企如何透過承包海外工程項目，不知不覺間混入中國本地來源不明的「過盛產能」，令工程隱患更加隱藏及難以有效監察，那麼發現石棉及鉛就也不令人意外。 (順帶一提，John Holland 也是沙中線工程醜聞的主角之一，但我們沒有資訊自由法逼使港鐵交出工程黑幕。)<br />\n<br />\n如果中資承包建築物料供應鏈，根本接二連三不斷出事，還要興建的是關乎性命安危的設施，為何到我們要興建更高安全系數的檢疫設施，都可以如此輕率繞過立法會直接批錢給劣跡斑斑的中資負責?<br />\n<br />\n#唔可以鉛量<br />\n#隔離營<br />\n#想病毒死石棉毒死定鉛水毒死<br />\n#細路都唔放過<br />\n#中交建威水史系列<br />\n#一帶一路<br />\n#資訊自由法好重要<br />\n<br />\n【註一】Tasmanian Times : Lead-Contaminated Water at RHH<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2TtDN09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TtDN09&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnEigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=a43ead27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2TtDN09</a><br />\n<br />\n【註二】The West Australian : High lead levels found in drinking water at new children's hospital<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/38vuWiM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38vuWiM&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnEigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=c70c3432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/38vuWiM</a><br />\n<br />\n【註三】出口物料含石棉 香港上市中資遠大 貨櫃遭澳洲邊防扣查 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/38rUDAR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38rUDAR&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnEigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=a6e9917e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/38rUDAR</a><br />\n<br />\n【註四】蘋果日報 : 一含鉛水辦來自內地預製廚房<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3avGlka\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3avGlka&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnEigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=81c77ddc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3avGlka</a><br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n🌎 支持中港研究工作<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us-2%2F&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnEigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=e7ef6cf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjtHFSA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjtHFSA.jpg&h=ceaf2fd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"499f62a46fecedd8e81f1aca9e779ce0edd47bac","tid":1913767,"uid":255105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:11:25.000Z","msg":"SOURCE: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2893776630718391/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063%2F2893776630718391%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnEigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=2cc0a3ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2893776630718391/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"b550af910dc65b52cded276a716c9737369daa58","tid":1913767,"uid":255105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"請支持本土研究社"},{"pid":"cef4066fe4c548ddf5097bd58c6cbdfb4e2c1d5a","tid":1913767,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:16:26.000Z","msg":"中資工程大法好，鉛水石棉一齊嘆，極速生癌不是夢，隔離營變往生營"},{"pid":"ab098fce3fc7698ae1124eae767f1ad9444b059f","tid":1913767,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3fbe1fc5b8679e99f7327fb3320b5619c55eb463","tid":1913767,"uid":42857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d5e2935e4289d1e30246d17b20353651b4774a","tid":1913767,"uid":136661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:23:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0661ef4252e708e281e81bca19a0db40a8f90898","tid":1913767,"uid":36920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:29:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b37d0d035bd23b3db03f206239b3a3441c5f8a76","tid":1913767,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:29:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"730e3acbd1fab9cf953837527239084152628bd2","tid":1913767,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e35e0ef79214eb8c6837f107d801cb124fdd95b","tid":1913767,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:30:48.000Z","msg":"仲要冇得揀  要隔離就要住入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdfe55b1b52b1f6169959ec4534b84d61a49fb6","tid":1913767,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}